name: Portrait Of The Hacker Typing
description: On June 28th 2021 it was discovered that an attacker had exploited a flaw in the hicetnunc swap contract, allowing them to swap more editions of an OBJKT than they owned. The hacker later joined the #🐛report-bugs channel on the hicetnunc Discord under the screen name hen-exploiter, taking responsibility for the hack. This is a portrait of hen-exploiter as most Discord users got to know him on that day. — Artist: Raphaël de Courville (@sableraph) — 14 frames at 1000 × 1000 pixels
